    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Download iTunes U Course - The Hacker Way]]></title>
    <link href="http://balta2ar.github.com/blog/2013/10/13/download-itunes-u-course-the-hacker-way/"/>
    <updated>2013-10-13T13:48:00+04:00</updated>
