</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>&lt;?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?&gt;
</span><span class='line'>&lt;feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:itms="http://www.itunes.com/dtds/itunesu-1.0.dtd"&gt;
